-to-receive-first-plane-at-end-of-july/00000190-9b89-d0d3-a5f3-9bb95c940000</guid></item><item><title>英国考虑撤销对国际刑事法院对以色列内塔尼亚胡和加兰特逮捕令的保留</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/u-k-considers-withdrawing-reservations-against-icc-warrants-for-netanyahu-and-gallant/00000190-9b7c-d360-abbf-9b7c70c80000</link><description>英国新政府正在考虑推翻前任里希·苏纳克政府的决定，并允许国际刑事法院继续对以色列高级官员发出逮捕令。新任外交大臣戴维·拉米下周首次访问以色列时将讨论这个话题</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:42:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/u-k-considers-withdrawing-reservations-against-icc-warrants-for-netanyahu-and-gallant/00000190-9b7c-d360-abbf-9b7c70c80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事调查发现 10 月 7 日贝埃里战役期间部队行为存在严重缺陷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-finds-serious-flaws-in-troops-conduct-during-beeri-battles-on-october-7/00000190-9965-d3c0-a7b0-f96587ec0000</link><description>调查结果将于周四公布，熟悉调查结果的消息人士表示，调查还将重点关注一名高级指挥官炮击一处关押着 13 名人质的房屋的决定</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 05:34:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-finds-serious-flaws-in-troops-conduct-during-beeri-battles-on-october-7/00000190-9965-d3c0-a7b0-f96587ec0000</guid></item><item><title>利库德集团内部人士认为，“不稳定”的本格维尔不太可能推翻内塔尼亚胡瘫痪的政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/unstable-ben-gvir-unlikely-to-bring-down-netanyahus-government-likud-insiders-believe/00000190-99a7-d3c0-a7b0-f9e75f200000</link><description>以色列极右翼国家安全部长似乎认为选举迫在眉睫，尽管他的行为鲁莽，但他的反对策略在民意调查中为他带来了良好的结果</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 03:00:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/unstable-ben-gvir-unlikely-to-bring-down-netanyahus-government-likud-insiders-believe/00000190-99a7-d3c0-a7b0-f9e75f200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队呼吁加沙城所有居民撤离